## P1: Secret Management (MUST HAVE)

### Problem
Secrets are scattered across env vars, config files, and systemd units. Production needs a unified secret management strategy.

### Work Required

| Task | Status | Owner |
|------|--------|-------|
| Deploy HashiCorp Vault or AWS Secrets Manager | 🔴 Not started | DevOps |
| Create secret rotation policy (90-day max age) | 🔴 Not started | Security |
| Audit all env vars for secret leakage in logs | 🔴 Not started | Agent B |
| Add secret masking to logging (`***` for keys) | 🔴 Not started | TBD |
| Implement `generate_dev_keys.py` for local dev | 🟡 Partial | Agent B |
| Add `detect-secrets` to CI (block on findings) | 🔴 Not started | TBD |

### Acceptance Criteria
- [ ] No plaintext secrets in repo, CI logs, or systemd units
- [ ] Secret rotation is documented and automated
- [ ] Local dev generates ephemeral keys automatically
- [ ] CI blocks any new committed secret

